</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0145-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0145-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>In the letter-book copy Arnold includes here the words except a few Battoes.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0145-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0145-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>Arnold sent a letter to Schuyler on this date by an Indian named Eneas. See <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Kenneth Roberts, ed. &lt;i&gt;March to Quebec: Journals of the Members of Arnolds Expedition&lt;/i&gt;. New York, 1938. ]">Roberts, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">March to Quebec</span></span>, 7071.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0145-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0145-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>The enclosed copy of Arnolds journal for 15 Sept.13 Oct. is in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>. For a printed version, see ibid., 4451.</p>

